享受吞云吐雾的快感

365
00:16:55,610 --> 00:16:57,400
Oh,that'll get you there.
喔 快活赛神仙

366
00:16:58,340 --> 00:17:00,050
Oh,that's good.
感觉真妙

367
00:17:00,050 --> 00:17:01,140
You want a drag?
来一口吗?

368
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:03,270
Can we be professionals? Please?
能专业点吗? 拜托?

369
00:17:03,270 --> 00:17:04,960
Yeah. Yeah,professionals?
对对 专业?

370
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,760
You know who's working the camera right now?
你知道谁在摄像吗?

371
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,270
A chair.
一把椅子

372
00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:11,230
We're on a show where we can't even get the cameraman to watch.
我们的节目甚至没有摄像师观看

373
00:17:11,230 --> 00:17:12,850
