所以我和你能在直播时抽烟

376
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,690
No,thank you.
不 谢了

377
00:17:21,690 --> 00:17:23,210
Why?
为什么?

378
00:17:23,210 --> 00:17:25,860
Because of our millions and millions of impressionable viewers?
因为我们数之不尽的敏感观众?

379
00:17:25,860 --> 00:17:27,220
Okay...
好吧

380
00:17:27,610 --> 00:17:30,810
If any impressionable viewers have a problem with this,please give us a call.
要是任何敏感的观众对此有意见 请拨打电话

381
00:17:30,810 --> 00:17:32,380
The number's on the screen.
号码在屏幕上

382
00:17:35,230 --> 00:17:37,960
Chirp,chirp? Chirp,chirp?
铃铃铃 铃铃铃?

383
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:41,290
Come on,Robin... live a little.
拜托 Robin...活出自我本色

384
00:17:52,950 --> 00:17:56,050
